lead_paragraph: Sixteen years after being an unused reserve at her home Sydney Olympics, Australian rider Sue Hearn will finally make her Games debut at the age of 60 in Rio.

headline.print_headline: Better Late Than Never, Pullout Hands Australian Hearn Rio Berth
